OL,3,CNottingham killings 'wholly
OL,4,Cavoidable', say victims' families
OL,5,Cafter review
OL,7,FSerious failings by the NHS trust
OL,8,Fwhich cared for Valdo Calocane shows
OL,9,Fit played down the risk he posed to
OL,10,Fothers ahead of his killing spree, as
OL,11,FITV News' Ben Chapman reports
OL,13,FThe families of three people killed by
OL,14,Fa paranoid schizophrenic on the
OL,15,Fstreets of Nottingham believe their
OL,16,Fdeaths could have been averted if the
OL,17,Fkiller's care was properly delivered.
