OL,3,CNottingham killings 'wholly
OL,4,Cavoidable', say victims' families
OL,5,Cafter review
OL,7,FA damning review by the Care Quality
OL,8,FCommission (CQC) has revealed a series
OL,9,Fof errors in Valdo Calocane's care
OL,10,Fmeant the public was put at risk by a
OL,11,Fparanoid schizophrenic refusing to
OL,12,Ftake his medication.
OL,14,FIt found risk assessments from
OL,15,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,16,FFoundation Trust (NHFT) played down
OL,17,Fthe fact he was having ongoing
OL,18,Fpsychosis and was violent to others
OL,19,Fwhen this was not managed well.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
