OL,4,Cavoidable', say victims' families
OL,5,Cafter review
OL,7,F"The deaths of our loved ones were
OL,8,Fentirely preventable, on multiple
OL,9,Foccasions," she told ITV News.
OL,11,F"Nottinghamshire Mental Health Trust
OL,12,Fhas failed us, the families, my son,
OL,13,Fmy son's friends. I don't think it's
OL,14,Fisolated in Nottinghamshire, I think
OL,15,Fit's systemic across the country."
OL,17,FShe reaffirmed a remark written in a
OL,18,Fjoint victim statement that medical
OL,19,Fprofessionals at Nottinghamshire have
OL,20,F"blood on their hands".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
