OL,7,F"Had they done their job properly
OL,8,FBarnaby would be alive today - I have
OL,9,Fno doubt about that," Emma Webber told
OL,10,FITV News
OL,12,F"Medical professionals who should know
OL,13,Fbetter, they were negligent in their
OL,14,Fwork and their jobs," she said.
OL,16,FMr Coates' son James, also spoke of
OL,17,Fthe review into Calocane's care.
