OL,7,F"If they'd just done the job a little
OL,8,Fbit better or properly, maybe Valdo's
OL,9,Ftrajectory, might have been put in a
OL,10,Fdifferent direction," he said.
OL,12,F"Or maybe he might have been inside
OL,13,Fand getting the help he needed before."
OL,15,FCalocane was diagnosed with
OL,16,Fschizophrenia three years before
OL,17,Flaunching his van and knife attack in
OL,18,FNottingham city centre and had been
OL,19,Fsectioned four times.
