OL,7,FOne of the failures listed by
OL,8,FTuesday's report highlights that risk
OL,9,Fassessments didn't make the danger he
OL,10,Fposed clear enough.
OL,12,FThe CQC report also questioned how
OL,13,Fwell the trust engaged with Calocane's
OL,14,Ffamily - as it found information from
OL,15,Fthem was not consistently acted upon.
OL,17,FThe parents of Grace O'Malley Kumar,
OL,18,Falso killed in the attack, believe
OL,19,Ftragedy could have been averted if
OL,20,FCalocane's care was properly delivered.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
