OL,7,F"Each time he was sectioned, his
OL,8,Ftreatment didn't change or people can
OL,9,Fbe bothered to change his treatment,"
OL,10,Fsaid Grace's father, Dr Sanjoy Kumar.
OL,12,F"I'm more than convinced that this was
OL,13,Fwholly avoidable if this person had
OL,14,Fbeen treated with any form of
OL,15,Fresponsibility whatsoever."
OL,17,FGrace's mother, Dr Sinead O'Malley,
OL,18,Fwants those in charge of his care to
OL,19,Fbe held fully responsible.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
