OL,7,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting has
OL,8,Fsaid Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,9,Fis "actively considering" how best to
OL,10,Fset up a judge-led inquiry into the
OL,11,FValdo Calocane case.
OL,13,F"There were so many failures that the
OL,14,Ffamilies of the victims have had to
OL,15,Fsuffer since these appalling
OL,16,Fhomicides," he said.
