OL,7,F"And that's why the Prime Minister,
OL,8,Fbefore the general election, committed
OL,9,Fto a judge-led inquiry looking at
OL,10,Ffailures not just in the NHS, but
OL,11,Fthroughout the criminal justice system
OL,12,Fas well.
