OL,7,F"Because what I've been really mindful
OL,8,Fof every time I've met the families is
OL,9,Fthat their ordeal and the pain that's
OL,10,Fbeen inflicted on them continued after
OL,11,Fthe deaths of their loved ones, and
OL,12,Fthat's because of failings and a lack
OL,13,Fof accountability, not just in the
OL,14,FNHS, but across the criminal justice
OL,15,Fsystem.
OL,17,F"That's why the Prime Minister is now
OL,18,Factively considering how that judge-
OL,19,Fled inquiry can best operate to
OL,20,Fdeliver the answers and the
OL,21,Faccountability the families need."
