OL,7,FA Nottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust spokesperson said:
OL,9,F"We acknowledge and accept the
OL,10,Fconclusions of this report and have
OL,11,Fsignificantly improved processes and
OL,12,Fstandards since the review was carried
OL,13,Fout."
OL,15,FClaire Murdoch, national director for
OL,16,Fmental health at NHS England, said:
OL,17,F"The CQC has identified unacceptable
OL,18,Ffailings in the care and treatment
OL,19,Fprovided to Valdo Calocane.
